      "instruction": "<p>Return the pot to a medium heat and add 20g <span class=\"text-purple\">[30g]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[40g]</span> <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Once melted, add 20g <span class=\"text-purple\">[30g]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [40g]</span> <strong>flour </strong>and stir with a wooden spoon for 1-2 min or until a sandy paste forms – this is your <strong>roux</strong></p><p>Gradually whisk 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[375ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml] </span><strong>milk </strong>into the roux,<strong> </strong>a little at a time, and cook for 5 min or until a smooth, thick sauce remains – this is your <strong>béchamel sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
