    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the pot from the heat and add your <strong>soft cheese</strong>, <strong>chicken stock mix</strong>, <strong>grated cheese</strong> and most of your <strong>dried basil</strong> (you'll use the rest later) and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Add a large splash of <strong>starchy pasta water </strong>with<strong> </strong>a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>creamy pasta sauce</strong></p>",
