    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>cooked chicken</strong>, <strong>cooked farfalle</strong>, most of the <strong>caramelised onion</strong> and <strong>spinach</strong> to the sauce and mix it all together</p><p>Transfer to an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>and top with the<strong> remaining caramelised onion</strong>, <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong>, the <strong>remaining dried basil</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Cook for 12-14 min or until the breadcrumbs are lightly golden – this is your <strong>creamy chicken breast & spinach farfalle bake</strong></p>",
